{
  "texts": [
    "Huawei's Pangu large CV model, which focuses on the intelligent inspection of unmanned aerial vehicle (UAV) power scenarios [179], addresses two main challenges.",
    "The first is efficient data labeling.",
    "They used massive amounts of unlabeled power data for pre-training and combined a small number of labeled samples for fine-tuning.",
    "This method increases the sample selection efficiency by approximately 30 times.",
    "The second challenge is generality and multidefect recognition."
  ]
}